        "left_accordion_yyajfm": {
          "type": "left_accordion",
          "settings": {
            "heading": "What can it do for your skin",
            "text": "<p>Helps reveal a smoother-looking, more radiant complexion. Formulated to help improve the appearance of dark spots and uneven tone for skin that looks refreshed and luminous.</p><p><strong>Skin Concerns:</strong> Ideal for skin that appears uneven in tone or texture and shows visible dark spots or post-blemish marks.</p>"
          }
        },
        "left_accordion_yxGEWq": {
          "type": "left_accordion",
          "settings": {
            "heading": "All Ingredients",
            "text": "<p><strong>Odycea Onsen-Sui Thermal Spring Water (France):</strong> Making up 50% of the formula, this mineral-rich thermal spring water is the foundation of our serum. Naturally sourced from the Onsen-Sui springs in France, it’s known for its soothing, hydrating, and balancing properties that help support skin comfort, barrier strength, and ingredient performance. As the main base of our micro-infusion system, it gives the formula its refreshing and lightweight feel — gentle enough even for sensitive skin.<br/><br/><strong>Epidermal Growth Factor (EGF):</strong> A science-backed ingredient known to support the look of smoother, hydrated, and more refreshed skin. Helps visibly reduce the look of fine lines and uneven tone.<br/><br/><strong>Niacinamide:</strong>A multi-benefit vitamin known to help improve the look of uneven tone, minimize visible pores, and support smoother-looking skin.<br/><br/><strong>Tranexamic Acid</strong>:A brightening ingredient that helps visibly improve the look of dark spots, uneven tone, and dullness.<br/><br/><strong>All ingredients</strong>: Odycea Onsen-Sui (Thermal water), Propanediol, Glycerin, Tranexamic Acid, Niacinamide, Panthenol, Chrysanthellum Indicum Extract, Ethylhexylglycerin, Tripeptide-1, Xanthan Gum, Allantoin, SH-Oligopeptide-1.</p><p><em>Please note that due to innovative updates and changing regulatory guidelines, the ingredient lists provided here may differ slightly from those on our packaging and distributor websites.</em></p>"
          }
        },
        "right_accordion_mDwXEE": {
          "type": "right_accordion",
          "settings": {
            "heading": "What can it do for your skin",
            "text": "<p>Delivers lasting hydration to leave skin looking plumper, smoother, and refreshed. Helps reduce the look of fine lines and wrinkles while supporting visibly calm, balanced, and supple-feeling skin.</p><p><strong>Skin Concerns:</strong> Ideal for skin that appears dry, dull, or shows visible signs of aging such as fine lines, uneven tone, and temporary redness.</p>"
          }
        },
        "right_accordion_e7UDEA": {
          "type": "right_accordion",
          "settings": {
            "heading": "All Ingredients",
            "text": "<p><strong>Odycea Onsen-Sui Thermal Spring Water (France): </strong>Making up 50% of the formula, this mineral-rich thermal spring water is the foundation of our serum. Naturally sourced from the Onsen-Sui springs in France, it’s known for its soothing, hydrating, and balancing properties that help support skin comfort, barrier strength, and ingredient performance. As the main base of our micro-infusion system, it gives the formula its refreshing and lightweight feel — gentle enough even for sensitive skin.<br/><br/><strong>Beta Glucan:</strong> A powerful hydrator that helps the skin feel supple, moisturized, and visibly smoother.<br/><br/><strong>GHK-Cu (Copper Peptide)</strong>:A peptide complex known to help improve the appearance of firmness and smoothness for youthful-looking skin. Gives the serum its signature blue hue.<br/><br/><strong>Sodium Hyaluronate:</strong>A powerful hydrator that helps the skin feel supple, moisturized, and visibly smoother.</p><p><strong>All ingredients:</strong></p><p>Odycea Onsen-Sui (Thermal water), Propanediol, Glycerin, Panthenol, Niacinamide, Myrothamnus Flabellifolia Leaf/Stem Extract, Water, Butylene Glycol, Hydroxyacetophenone, Copper Tripeptide-1, Beta-Glucan, Chrysanthellum Indicum Extract, Ethylhexylglycerin, Allantoin, Sodium Hyaluronate, Xanthan Gum.</p><p><em>Please note that due to innovative updates and changing regulatory guidelines, the ingredient lists provided here may differ slightly from those on our packaging and distributor websites.</em></p>"
          }
        }
